    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition example that presents beautifully and appears to have been very well cared for throughout. The exterior shows clean, glossy paint with strong trim and glass, and the interior is equally impressive with a fresh, well-kept appearance. This is the kind of car that should satisfy a buyer looking for a standout, turnkey example rather than a project or driver-quality car.",
