      "description": "$5,900 - Honest project classic with plenty of vintage character and a great opportunity for the right buyer. This car is in poor condition and will need significant work before it can be considered road-ready, but it could make a worthwhile restoration candidate or parts car for someone looking for an affordable entry point into a classic. A straightforward, no-surprises listing for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
