      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "A great budget-friendly car for someone who wants dependable basic transportation or a solid project to tinker with. It\u2019s not perfect, but it has a lot of life left for the right buyer and offers a comfortable ride, practical space, and real value without breaking the bank. If you\u2019re looking for an honest, affordable vehicle and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, this one could be a fantastic fit.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong-running project car with a willing powertrain, solid road presence, and plenty of usable life for the right buyer. The engine fires up, pulls cleanly, and the drivetrain feels mechanically honest, making this a great budget commuter, parts donor, or weekend fixer-upper. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present, but the core package still offers value for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at. Priced to move and worth a look if you want affordable entry into a capable platform.",
